---
import MainLayout from '../../layouts/MainLayout.astro';
import '../../styles/article.css';
---

<MainLayout 
  title="Tentang Naufal Muhammad Al Hikam"
  description="Personal Blogger, Storyteller, & Life Learner. Berbagi tentang perjalanan belajar, teknologi, dan mindfulness."
>
  <article class="article-content bio-container">
    <div class="bio-header">
      <div class="bio-avatar">
        <img src="/naufalmuhammadalhikam.jpg" alt="Naufal Muhammad Al Hikam" />
      </div>
      <h1 class="article-title">Naufal Muhammad Al Hikam</h1>
      <p class="bio-tagline">Personal Blogger, Storyteller, & Life Learner</p>
      
      <div class="social-links">
        <a href="https://facebook.com" class="social-item fb" aria-label="Facebook" target="_blank">
          <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M18 2h-3a5 5 0 0 0-5 5v3H7v4h3v8h4v-8h3l1-4h-4V7a1 1 0 0 1 1-1h3z"></path></svg>
        </a>
        <a href="https://instagram.com" class="social-item ig" aria-label="Instagram" target="_blank">
          <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><rect x="2" y="2" width="20" height="20" rx="5" ry="5"></rect><path d="M16 11.37A4 4 0 1 1 12.63 8 4 4 0 0 1 16 11.37z"></path><line x1="17.5" y1="6.5" x2="17.51" y2="6.5"></line></svg>
        </a>
        <a href="https://linkedin.com" class="social-item li" aria-label="LinkedIn" target="_blank">
          <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M16 8a6 6 0 0 1 6 6v7h-4v-7a2 2 0 0 0-2-2 2 2 0 0 0-2 2v7h-4v-7a6 6 0 0 1 6-6z"></path><rect x="2" y="9" width="4" height="12"></rect><circle cx="4" cy="4" r="2"></circle></svg>
        </a>
        <a href="https://threads.net" class="social-item th" aria-label="Threads" target="_blank">
           <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M12 12c0-3 3-5 5-5s5 2 5 5v3c0 3-2 5-5 5s-5-2-5-5z"></path><path d="M12 7c-3 0-5 2-5 5s2 5 5 5"></path><path d="M7 12c0 3-2 5-5 5"></path></svg>
        </a>
        <a href="https://wa.me/yournumber" class="social-item wa" aria-label="WhatsApp" target="_blank">
          <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M22 16.92v3a2 2 0 0 1-2.18 2 19.79 19.79 0 0 1-8.63-3.07 19.5 19.5 0 0 1-6-6 19.79 19.79 0 0 1-3.07-8.67A2 2 0 0 1 4.11 2h3a2 2 0 0 1 2 1.72 12.84 12.84 0 0 0 .7 2.81 2 2 0 0 1-.45 2.11L8.09 9.91a16 16 0 0 0 6 6l1.27-1.27a2 2 0 0 1 2.11-.45 12.84 12.84 0 0 0 2.81.7A2 2 0 0 1 22 16.92z"></path></svg>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="article-body">
      <p class="lead">
        Halo! Saya Naufal. Di Mentari Muda, saya berbagi tentang perjalanan belajar, 
        pemanfaatan teknologi dengan bijak, serta seni menjalani hidup dengan lebih sadar (mindfulness).
      </p>
      
      <p>
        Saya percaya bahwa setiap orang memiliki cerita yang layak dibagikan dan setiap pengalaman 
        adalah guru yang berharga. Melalui tulisan, saya berusaha untuk memproses pemikiran 
        dan merangkai makna dari keseharian yang kita jalani.
      </p>

      <h2>Misi Saya</h2>
      <p>
        Membangun Mentari Muda bukan sekadar hobi, melainkan misi untuk menciptakan ruang digital 
        yang sehat. Di tengah riuhnya informasi, saya rindu akan tulisan yang mengajak kita 
        berhenti sejenak dan berpikir lebih dalam.
      </p>

      <h2>Mari Terhubung</h2>
      <p>
        Jika Anda ingin berdiskusi atau sekadar menyapa, silakan hubungi saya melalui kanal sosial media di atas. 
        Saya selalu terbuka untuk perspektif baru dan obrolan yang bermakna.
      </p>
    </div>
  </article>
</MainLayout>

<style>
  .bio-container {
    padding-top: 2rem;
  }

  .bio-header {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 3.5rem;
    padding-bottom: 2.5rem;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
  }

  .bio-avatar {
    width: 120px;
    height: 120px;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #FF6B6B 0%, #FF8E53 100%);
    border-radius: 50%;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    margin: 0 auto 1.5rem;
    overflow: hidden;
    box-shadow: 0 15px 35px rgba(255, 107, 107, 0.25);
    border: 3px solid white;
  }

  .bio-avatar img {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    object-fit: cover;
  }

  .bio-tagline {
    font-size: 1.15rem;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    margin-top: -0.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .social-links {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: 16px;
    margin-top: 24px;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }

  .social-item {
    width: 44px;
    height: 44px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    border-radius: 12px;
    background: var(--sidebar-bg);
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    transition: all 0.3s cubic-bezier(0.175, 0.885, 0.32, 1.275);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
  }

  .social-item:hover {
    transform: translateY(-5px);
    color: white;
    border-color: transparent;
    box-shadow: 0 10px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
  }

  .social-item.fb:hover { background: #1877F2; }
  .social-item.ig:hover { background: linear-gradient(45deg, #f09433 0%, #e6683c 25%, #dc2743 50%, #cc2366 75%, #bc1888 100%); }
  .social-item.li:hover { background: #0077b5; }
  .social-item.th:hover { background: #000000; }
  .social-item.wa:hover { background: #25D366; }

  @media (max-width: 640px) {
    .bio-avatar {
      width: 100px;
      height: 100px;
      font-size: 2.5rem;
    }
    
    .bio-tagline {
       font-size: 1rem;
    }
  }
</style>
